        <
        min
        (
        R
        ,
        2
        
          
            R
          
        
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle \beta <\min(R,2{\sqrt {R}})}
   and 
  
    
      
        
          β
          

          
          

          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \beta _{}^{}}
   is a positive integer that can take multiple values at a given 
  
    
      
        R
      
    
    {\displaystyle R}
  . For 
  
    
      
        β
