    {\displaystyle {\begin{array}{lll}Z_{2}^{\mathbb {N} }&\to &[0,1)\\\left(x_{k}\right)_{k\in \mathbb {N} }&\mapsto &\sum _{k\geq 1}x_{k}2^{-k}\end{array}}}
  both surjective, which give rise to a surjective (thus space-filling) mapping

  
    
      
        [
        0
